These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-9-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, collecting, reading, drawing
The people have 4 different jobs:  lawyer, security-guard, project-manager, pilot
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, pop, classical, disco
 1. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is drawing##3
 2. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is collecting##3
 3. the fan classical is not to the right of the fan pop##8
 4. the fan pop is not to the left of the pilot##8
 5. the person who's hobby is video-games is in an even position##4
 6. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the fan classical##1
 7. the lawyer is the fan house##1
 8. the fan classical is not the pilot##6
 9. the fan pop is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is reading##5
10. the person who's hobby is reading is not to the right of the project-manager##8
11. the person who's hobby is collecting is not to the left of the person who's hobby is reading##8
12. the fan pop is between the person who's hobby is reading and the security-guard##2
13. the fan classical and the project-manager have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2        |     3     |    4    |
| Hobby         | reading | collecting      | drawing | video-games |
| Job           | project-manager | pilot | security-guard      | lawyer |
| Music-Genre   | classical        | pop            | disco    | house |

