.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-9-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, almond-milk, lemonade, soy-milk
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: soul, hip-hop, house, rock
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, badminton, parkour, weightlifting
 1. the fan house is not to the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##8
 2. the person drinking almond-milk is not to the right of the person drinking lemonade##8
 3. the person who's sport is badminton and the fan soul have the same parity positions##9
 4. the fan house is somewhere to the right of the fan rock##5
 5. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 6. the person drinking mirinda is not to the left of the person drinking almond-milk##8
 7. the fan rock is not to the right of the person drinking soy-milk##8
 8. the person who's sport is badminton is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person drinking lemonade##2
 9. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the fan hip-hop##1
10. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the fan rock##1
11. the fan soul is not to the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##8
12. the fan rock is not to the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##8
13. the fan rock is on the left of the fan house##1
14. the fan house is not to the left of the person drinking soy-milk##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2   |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | mirinda   | lemonade     | soy-milk     |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop    | soul   | rock      | house    |
| Sport         | weightlifting   | badminton | parkour | lacrosse |

