.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-9-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, reading, card-games, chess
There are 4 different nationalities: german, russian, canadian, thai
4 different pets are kept: ferret, hedgehog, frog, rat
 1. the person who's hobby is baking is not to the left of the german##8
 2. the canadian is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
 3. the canadian is the person who's hobby is baking##1
 4. the canadian is somewhere between the thai and the owner of the hedgehog##7
 5. the person who's hobby is chess and the german have different parity positions##9
 6. the owner of the frog is not to the right of the person who's hobby is baking##8
 7. the owner of the frog is somewhere to the left of the thai##5
 8. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is chess##5
 9. the russian is on the left of the german##1
10. the owner of the ferret is between the german and the owner of the rat##2
11. the person who's hobby is reading is not the german##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |    4    |
| Hobby         | chess | card-games     | baking  | reading |
| Nationality   | russian       | german    | canadian | thai |
| Pet           | frog       | hedgehog | ferret     | rat  |

