.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-9-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, mirinda, tea, sprite
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, video-games, skydiving, traveling
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, biathlon, tennis, swimming
 1. the person drinking tea and the person who's hobby is skydiving have the same parity positions##9
 2. the person who's sport is parkour and the person who's hobby is video-games have different parity positions##9
 3. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 4. the person who's hobby is video-games is somewhere to the left of the person drinking soy-milk##5
 5. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
 6. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
 7. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 8. the person who's hobby is fishing is the person who's sport is parkour##1
 9. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##5
10. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the person who's sport is tennis and the person who's hobby is skydiving##2
11. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the person who's sport is biathlon##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2      |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage   | sprite  | soy-milk        | tea  | mirinda |
| Hobby      | video-games  | fishing    | skydiving | traveling |
| Sport      | tennis | parkour | swimming | biathlon    |

